  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 04/04/2022 at 11:30pm CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.18.3-MinorChanges\">Minor Changes</h3><ul><li><p>Improved Square Integration so that it requires logging in with the correct credentials, even if a user was previously logged into Square on that browser session.</p></li><li><p>Improved the Square Integration's UI for clarity, based on client feedback.</p></li><li><p>On the Cash Reconciliation page, separated &quot;payment amount&quot; and &quot;tip amount from&quot; in the Gateway Transactions list, for clarity.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.3-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>For the Square Integration, resolved an issue where the &quot;Tip First&quot; and &quot;Tip Last&quot; options were not working correctly.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue where trying to download a Ticket Approval redirected the user to a failure error page.</p></li><li><p>Resolved behavior on internal purchase orders where items rejected on the order would still create unwanted items in &quot;Backordered&quot; status.</p></li><li><p>For certain customers utilizing GSX service programs, implemented multiple bug fixes for the FedEx integration, especially resolving an issue where the RMA Tracking page being filtered for &quot;sent&quot; items caused an Error500.</p></li><li><p>Resolved a problem where clicking the Import Compatibility download button would not do anything.</p></li><li><p>Fixed a bug where uploading Branding Images worked inconsistently.</p></li><li><p>Fixed a bug where replacing Branding Images worked inconsistently.</p></li><li><p>Fixed a bug where In some cases, Catalog Items would not display under the correct category tree in Qsite.</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
